    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Junker Queen throws Jagged Blade to pull a target in or set up a follow-up throw, then leans on Adrenaline Rush's wound-based lifesteal to win extended trades at point-blank range.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her sustain depends entirely on landing damage; against poke comps that never let her into melee range, Adrenaline Rush heals almost nothing.</p>"
